Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:14.89,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:15.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:18.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:22.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:26.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:30.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:34.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:40.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:45.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:51.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.22,0:00:54.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:59.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:03.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:15.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:18.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We've received the mummy\NEgyptas from the Egypt Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:50.92,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,190.389)}The Revived Mummy Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:50.92,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs185\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,660.389)}Egyptas
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin Egyptas's life\Nforce transfer surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:02:00.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker had found the 4000-year-old\NEgyptian mummy Egyptas in a pyramid,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:05.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and brought it back to life, in order to\Nsearch for gemstones valued at one billion yen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:10.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,that the pharaoh Thutmose III\Nwas said to have sent to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:16.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Several days passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The life transfer surgery was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Egyptas, you have awakened\Nfrom a 4000-year slumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise, and show me your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:02:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Egyptas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have the gemstones,\Nworth one billion yen in modern currency,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,been sent to in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you, Egyptas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in Japan are the\None-billion-yen gemstones?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me. Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps Egyptas can understand\NJapanese, but cannot speak it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ancient Egyptian, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Computer, identify someone\Nwho can decipher ancient Egyptian
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring them to our base.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Egyptas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Egyptian monster that\Nlived back in 1800 BC?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Accompany us to our base,\Nand we'll spare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:04:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... are you the ones\Nwho killed Doctor Nishida?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Egyptas. Colonel Zol wants him alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Report it to Colonel Zol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:35.58,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an09\fs55\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H656835&}Kenzo Goda
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa! Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Phone call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear... sorry about that, Yuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Goda... it's Egyptas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Egyptas has returned to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What? E-Egyptas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:05:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He took out Doctor Nishida, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why is Egyptas after us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. But I suspect you're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ono! Ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji, go back to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Nighty-night, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ono, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these symbols?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They found the same symbols next\Nto the history professor Doctor Nishida,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,who was killed last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this his ID?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a history professor, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The burns... the circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a perfect match\Nfor last night's incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, there's been another murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Another murder? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigate those strange symbols found next\Nto Doctor Nishida when he died last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hayato... if you think you\Ncan leave me out of the loop here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.74,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&}Mysterious Late-Night Residential Death\NJonan University Instructor Nishida\NStrange Symbols Left at Scene
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange symbols left at the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what do these symbols mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible. That 4000-year-old monster\NEgyptas, back to life and here in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa! Help me! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Yuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Goda, your son Yuji\Nis in the custody of Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, we wish you to interpret\Nthe ancient Egyptian spoken by Egyptas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'd help Egyptas after\Nhe killed Nishida and Ono?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd do better not to resist, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the television.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say now, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Please don't hurt Yuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji will remain alive until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to make your mind up by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that understood, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently it means "fire-breathing\Nmonster Egyptas" in ancient Egyptian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a monster believed\Nto have lived 4000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That means Shocker's probably\Nbehind the murders, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:09:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's found and revived a\N4000-year-old monster from ancient Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And their objective is...\Na total mystery, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster from 4000 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels so unreal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But, there's something\Na bit romantic about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuri. This is no\Ntime for that nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But the monster would know things\Nthat happened 4000 years ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It could reveal to us the\Nmysteries of ancient Egypt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us speak ancient Egyptian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course... the hieroglyphs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now. That's our key.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head to Doctor Goda's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The two victims were both historians.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Goda was an authority on ancient\NEgypt with a similar level of renown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice work, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker will surely be after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Blasted Shocker...\NI guess they're not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Egyptas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let you take Doctor Goda!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Doctor Goda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Doctor Goda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:17.21,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Goda...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you please tell us\Nwhy is Shocker after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I d-don't have the slightest idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But they were trying to take you\Naway just minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor... please, talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Shocker planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they using Egyptas for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Egyptas?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know about him, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He was taken by Egyptas last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker kidnapped your child?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find any clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:21.10,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,"Papa, come save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:24.53,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,If you don't come, they'll kill me."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Taki!\N- Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're injured. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay with the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Not much to write home about...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:14:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We've captured Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:03.76,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,"Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:06.75,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I appreciate all you've done for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:12.29,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,And I'm sorry for the trouble you went\Nto, but I'm going to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:14.96,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Please understand, Ichimonji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.27,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,This is the only option I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:23.02,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,If I don't go, Shocker may kill Yuji."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No one here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You've returned, Egyptas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would the doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker! Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They've stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten kilometers to the east-southeast...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yuji!\N- Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, kindly do your work first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, doctor... interpret at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about, Yuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be safe soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"18th Pharaoh of Egypt, Thutmose III,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,hid his gemstone hoard\Nin a country far to the north..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? Where in that country?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"H-He respected the Tribe of Yezo\Nand showed friendship to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The hiding place of the gemstones\Nis known only to the head of the Yezo."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tribe of Yezo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So the gems worth one billion yen\Nare with the Yezo people of Hokkaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor... you've done your job perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no longer useful to Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.35,0:18:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And those who useless to Shocker must die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Yuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do to Yuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll kill him as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor... what happened to Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Hayato, the man who was with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Egyptas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Blow up this base, fly to\NHokkaido with the combatants,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and search for those gemstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I knock out Ichimonji,\Nwho was only trying to protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No time for self-recrimination, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Two kilometers left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When did that get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come quickly, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, they're on their way to Haneda!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Cyclone could make it. Go after them, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will defeat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Face me, Egyptas!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's taking all my concentration\Njust to dodge his attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get in closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.13,0:22:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.74,0:22:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.42,0:22:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I won! I finally beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.75,0:23:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.47,0:23:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I sometimes forget how\Nbrave parents can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a strange person, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.03,0:23:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You always seem to look on the bright side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:32.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato, the Kamen Rider,\Ndefeated the mummy monster, Egyptas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:36.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But more terrible battles with\NShocker would await him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:40.48,Cont,,0,60,155,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:43.90,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:45.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.82,0:23:47.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the poison gas Monster Torikabuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.64,0:23:51.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's vicious poison gas plan\Nputs Goro and friends in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.17,0:23:52.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider struggles to keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:55.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A deathmatch unfolds\Non a high-rise apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.51,0:24:01.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "Poison\NGas Monster Torikabuto's Operation G."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:24:01.19,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fscy80\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,210.389)}Poison Gas Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:24:01.19,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,680.389)}Torikabuto's Operation G
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.21,0:24:11.05,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.63,0:24:13.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.63,0:24:15.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.59,0:24:18.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.14,0:24:21.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.01,0:24:22.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.89,0:24:24.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.68,0:24:26.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.48,0:24:28.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.57,0:24:34.24,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.24,0:24:37.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.82,0:24:41.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.91,0:24:45.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Revived Mummy Monster, Egyptas